title: Nymeria: Part 2 - Ten Thousand Ships (video) (2018)
description:
A project with this exact name "Ten Thousand Ships" is in development at HBO as of 2021. GRRM's version of the Odyssey is here! We've got Brindled Men, wyverns, killer diseases, ancient cities, corsairs, dark gods... Plus characters like Daenerys, Missandei and her brothers, Victarion, Barristan Selmy, and his new knights. Video available on Spotify. Originally published Nov 24th 2018.
